#: ../../S/slurp.rst:5
msgid "slurp"
msgstr "slurp"

#: ../../S/slurp.rst:7
msgid "vt\\."
msgstr "他動詞"

#: ../../S/slurp.rst:9
msgid ""
"To read a large data file entirely into :ref:`core` before working on it. "
"This may be contrasted with the strategy of reading a small piece at a time,"
" processing it, and then reading the next piece. \"This program slurps in a "
"1K-by-1K matrix and does an FFT.\" See also :ref:`sponge`\\."
msgstr ""
"大きなデータファイルを、それに取りかかる前に\\ :ref:`core`\\ "
"にまるごと読み込むこと。これは、小さな断片を一度に読み、それを処理し、それから次の断片を読むという戦略と対比される。「このプログラムは1K×1Kの行列をslurpして、FFTを行う。」\\"
" :ref:`sponge`\\ も参照。"
